477
00:30:34,600 --> 00:30:38,200
My father always said trouble follows
that family like stink on a fly's ass.

478
00:30:38,300 --> 00:30:41,500
- Stay away from that girl.
- You don't need to take care of us, Amma.

479
00:30:41,600 --> 00:30:44,800
- I promised your mother and I want to.
- No, I d... Amma.

480
00:30:44,900 --> 00:30:47,400
I'm sorry, I just...

481
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:50,300
I don't think it's any of your business.

482
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,200
Where'd you get that?

483
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:56,900
- I don't know.
- Don't lie to me.

484
00:30:57,100 --> 00:30:58,500
What's wrong?

485
00:30:59,800 --> 00:31:01,600
You listen to me.

486
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:04,800
You go and bury that in Greenbrier
and forget you ever found it.

487
00:31:06,700 --> 00:31:09,600
I never said I was in Greenbrier, Amma.

488
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:55,400
What?

