00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:29,000
We do different things.

495
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:31,700
So, like, what, you're from Europe?

496
00:33:40,600 --> 00:33:44,800
You know how some families are musical
and some have money.

497
00:33:44,900 --> 00:33:47,200
Well, we have powers.

498
00:33:48,500 --> 00:33:50,000
Powers?

499
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:52,100
Yeah.

500
00:33:58,700 --> 00:34:00,200
What was that out there?

501
00:34:00,300 --> 00:34:03,600
That was Macon. He had the house bound.

502
00:34:03,700 --> 00:34:06,100
It's a spell to protect me when he's not here.

503
00:34:06,300 --> 00:34:07,300
A Spell?

504
00:34:07,500 --> 00:34:10,400
- Yeah. It won't happen again.
- Okay.

505
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,100
Lena...

506
00:34:13,500 --> 00:34:14,700
