507
00:34:14,700 --> 00:34:15,800
No.

508
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:18,300
(SIGHS)

509
00:34:20,500 --> 00:34:23,700
I mean, calling us "witches"
is like calling the smart kids "geeks"...

510
00:34:23,800 --> 00:34:25,400
...or the athletes "jocks."

511
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:27,500
We prefer the term "Caster."

512
00:34:28,400 --> 00:34:32,000
I didn't mean to break those windows.
My powers are getting stronger.

513
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:35,100
I can't always control it.

514
00:34:36,500 --> 00:34:38,600
You look nauseous.

515
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:42,000
You want a cookie? The sugar will help.

516
