I made these last night.

517
00:34:45,900 --> 00:34:47,600
From a cookie mix.

518
00:34:51,300 --> 00:34:52,700
Okay, what about this?

519
00:34:52,900 --> 00:34:54,500
I don't know.

520
00:34:54,700 --> 00:34:55,900
You don't know?

521
00:34:56,200 --> 00:34:58,200
No, it wasn't me.

522
00:34:59,000 --> 00:35:02,600
I mean, it was something else.
Something happens when we both hold it.

523
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:04,000
Okay, hold on a minute.

524
00:35:04,500 --> 00:35:07,500
Satan has nothing to do with y'all, right?

525
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,300
That is such a mortal thing to say.

526
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:14,700
- God.
- Well, there is evil, Lena.

527
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:17,700
Yes, there are evil Casters, Ethan.

528
00:35:17,900 --> 00:35:21,200
I mean, are you trying to say
that there are no evil mortals?

529
00:35:22,000 --> 00:35:26,200
Only difference is, you all made up
somebody else to blame for it.

530
00:35:32,700 --> 00:35:34,500
I'm just trying to figure this out.

531
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:37,600
So you have powers, okay?
What else can you do?

532
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:48,900
LENA: I collect poetry.

533
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:13,700
I'm not meant to show a mortal any of this.

534
00:36:13,800 --> 00:36:16,600
- It's okay.
- No, I shouldn't have.

535
00:36:20,400 --> 00:36:23,200
You know, I just hate hiding all the time.

536
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:27,500
Feeling like everybody's
whispering about me.

537
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:32,400
Being afraid of people
finding out I'm this freak.

538
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:36,700
Sometimes, you just want to be normal.

