00:36:41,700 --> 00:36:43,400
What are you smiling at?

541
00:36:43,500 --> 00:36:48,500
Lena, you're a miracle.
Why would you ever want to be normal?

542
00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:04,400
You're not what I expected.

543
00:37:04,600 --> 00:37:06,100
What do you mean?

544
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:09,100
Don't get mad,
but I've dreamt about you too.

545
00:37:10,600 --> 00:37:13,000
I just didn't think you were real.

546
00:37:13,600 --> 00:37:15,900
MACON: - Lena?
- Oh, it's Macon. You've gotta go.

547
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,900
Why didn't you tell me?

548
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:19,900
Scares me.

549
00:37:20,600 --> 00:37:21,700
Doesn't it scare you?

550
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:24,200
You wanna go outwith me?

551
00:37:24,400 --> 00:37:26,000
(BOTH CHUCKLE)

552
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:30,500
