553
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,300
Whoa, can you make anything grow?

554
00:37:42,500 --> 00:37:44,600
MACON: - Lena?
- Get out.

555
00:37:48,100 --> 00:37:51,000
- How about Friday, movies?
