1466
01:45:31,700 --> 01:45:34,600
Lena, I'm sorry, I didn't mean it.

1467
01:45:34,800 --> 01:45:36,300
Okay?

1468
01:45:36,900 --> 01:45:38,100
(GRUNTS)

1469
01:45:40,100 --> 01:45:46,200
Welcome to the family,
my darling, special girl.

1470
